SCOS INTEGRATION CLAUSE (CRITICAL)
===============================================================================

This project integrates with SCOS (Secure City Operating System) Intent Core.

SCOS is a joint project with shared rights. Any use of AEON Core that involves:
- SCOS bridge modules (scos-bridge/)
- Intent validation protocols
- Safety layer integrations

REQUIRES:
1. Prior written notification to the author: scos_system2026@mail.ru
2. Description of intended use case and deployment context
3. Agreement to maintain SCOS safety constraints without modification
4. Attribution to both AEON Core and SCOS Intent Core projects

SCOS-related code cannot be:
- Separated from its safety validation logic
- Modified to bypass intent checking
- Used in systems that do not respect consciousness continuity principles

